               <item n="m_remarks_old">&lt;p&gt;According to [[Broomhead I]]: 240 "[w]ritten in small to medium ductus, and very clearly preserved, it is the left edge of a five line manuscript with the number '89' on the verso".&lt;/p&gt;</item>
